Tachyon: A terminal faster than light!

Tachyon combines the terminal multiplexing festures of gnuscreen and tmux with the local echo prediction of mosh. 

The Tachyon bug tracker can be found at http://travisbrown.ca/projects/tachyon/issues/index.html

The test suite uses Lousy to run. Lousy can be found at https://github.com/travisb-ca/lousy

The Tachyon mailing list is tachyon@travisbrown.ca and the list archive and information can be found at http://lists.travisbrown.ca/listinfo.cgi/tachyon-travisbrown.ca
